general.name: mos_target_tic_v8
general.description: The Eighth version (v8.0) of the TESS Input Catalogue (). This catalogue is used in v0.5 target selection as a form of internal cross-match between the objects found in difference input catalogues.

surveys.name: BHM
surveys.description: An optical time-domain spectroscopic survey of quasars and X-ray sources

surveys.name: MWM
surveys.description: A time-domain, optical+IR spectroscopic survey of Milky Way stars of all types.

general.naming_convention: $MOS_TARGET/[V_TARG]/mos_tic_v8-[NUM].fits, where V_TARG=1.0.1 for DR18; and NUM = 1..1 to partition the file into parts

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
